section_label: Three images showing different views of the proper
raw_md_fragment:
[IMAGE]
Three images showing different views of the property:
1. A side view of the building showing a narrow alleyway and adjacent residential properties.
1. A rear view showing a parking area with several vehicles.
1. A close-up of the building's utility meters mounted on the exterior wall.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a stairwell with brick walls and mailboxes on the right side. The stairwell has a carpeted floor and metal railings.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a hallway with a wooden door and a painting on the wall. The hallway has a carpeted floor and metal railings.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a brick apartment building exterior with a red awning over the entrance. The building has multiple windows with air conditioning units.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a stairwell with a painting on the wall and carpeted steps. The stairwell has metal railings and brick walls.
[/IMAGE]
